title: Fareed.Zakaria.GPS.07.12.2009. CNN PDTV.XviD~Ekolb
description:
A GPS EXCLUSIVE with U.S. Secretary of Treasury Tim Geithner on the economic crisis. Did those green shoots we were seeing turn brown? And is Geithner doing enough to fix the problem?

Plus, one of the biggest thorns in Prime Minister Putin's side. Obama quietly met with him in Russia this week. You'll hear from the leader of the Russian opposition, Boris Nemtsov.
